种族清洗学者{{link-en|亚当·琼斯 (加拿大作家)|Adam Jones (Canadian scholar)|亚当·琼斯}}声称“人类经历的记录中很少有暴行可與1917年，[[布尔什维克|布尔什维克]]夺权政权後，到1953年斯大林去世，苏联转向較為约束且很大程度上不是那麼殘忍的國內政策之間引發的暴行相比。”他指出红色高棉（相对而言）及毛泽东统治下的中国（绝对而言）是其中的例外。<ref>[[#Jones2010Genocide|Jones (2010) ''Genocide'']] p. 124.</ref>

====红色恐怖====
{{Main|红色恐怖|去哥萨克化|列宁手令}}

[[俄国内战|俄国内战]]期间，双方都作出过恐怖活动（[[红色恐怖|红色]]和{{link-en|白色恐怖 (俄国)|White Terror (Russia)|白色恐怖}}）。红色恐怖通过政治警察[[契卡|契卡]]将数以万计的“[[阶级敌人|阶级敌人]]”[[就地正法|就地正法]]。<ref name="Melgunov">[[Sergei_Melgunov|Sergei Petrovich Melgunov]], ''The Red Terror in Russia'', Hyperion Pr (1975), ISBN 0-88355-187-X. {{Page needed|date=2011年6月}}<!-- no page to verify against-->;<br />See also: S. Melgunoff (1927) "[http://www.paulbogdanor.com/left/soviet/redterror.pdf The Record of the Red Terror] {{Wayback|url=http://www.paulbogdanor.com/left/soviet/redterror.pdf|date=20181221170529}}" ''Current History'' unknown volume and edition (pp. 198–205) at unknown page.{{Copyvio link}}{{Volume needed|date=2011年6月}}</ref>{{Copyvio link}}{{Volume needed|date=2011年6月}}<ref>[[W._Bruce_Lincoln|Lincoln, W. Bruce]], ''Red Victory: A History of the Russian Civil War'' (1999) [[Da_Capo_Press|Da Capo Press]].[//books.google.com/books?id=R6HAJIJhNp4C&pg=PA383 pp. 383–385] ISBN 0-306-80909-5.</ref><ref>{{Cite book|last=Leggett |first=George |title=The Cheka: Lenin's Political Police |publisher=[[牛津大学出版社|牛津大学出版社]] |year=1987 |pages=197–198 |isbn=0-19-822862-7}}</ref><ref>[[#Figes1997PeoplesTragedy|Figes (1997) ''A People's Tragedy'']] p. 647.</ref>當中许多牺牲者是被围捕的“[[资产阶级|资产阶级]]人质”後被其[[就地正法|就地正法]]以报复任何所谓的[[反革命|反革命]]挑衅。<ref>[[#Figes1997PeoplesTragedy|Figes (1997) ''A People's Tragedy'']] p. 643.</ref>许多人在镇压反抗中处死，像是[[喀琅施塔得起义|喀琅施塔得起义]]和[[坦波夫起义|坦波夫起义]]。{{le|唐纳德·雷菲尔德|Donald Rayfield}}教授声称“仅喀琅施塔得和坦波夫之后的镇压就有数以万计的人被处决。”<ref>{{le|唐纳德·雷菲尔德|Donald Rayfield}}. ''[[Stalin_and_His_Hangmen|Stalin and His Hangmen]]: The Tyrant and Those Who Killed for Him.'' [[Random_House|Random House]], 2004. ISBN 0-375-50632-2. [//books.google.com/books?id=Yi3ow3TU8-4C&pg=RA2-PA1915&lpg=RA2-PA1915&dq=the+repression+that+followed+the+rebellions+in+Kronstadt+and+Tambov+alone+resulted+in+tens+of+thousands+of+executions&source=bl&ots=ybz-v9e9rM&sig=KiiC5ploofzkKkiE_Z1pfmWg72g&hl=en&ei=EN4rS5uMBJKXtgevxtT_CA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CAgQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=the%20repression%20that%20followed%20the%20rebellions%20in%20Kronstadt%20and%20Tambov%20alone%20resulted%20in%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20executions&f=false p. 85]</ref>不少东正教牧师也被杀死。<ref name="Yakovlev">[[#Yakovlev2002CenturyofViolence|Yakovlev (2002) ''Century of Violence'']] p. 156.</ref><ref name="Pipes">[[Richard_Pipes|Richard Pipes]]. ''Russia Under the Bolshevik Regime.'' Vintage Books, 1994 ISBN 0-679-76184-5. pg 356</ref>

{{le|尼古拉斯·魏斯|Nicolas Werth}}指，去哥萨克化政策其實是[[苏联|苏联]]领导人對“排除、[[种族灭绝|消灭]]并驱逐整个地区的人口”的嘗試。<ref>Nicolas Werth "A State against its People: violence, repression, and terror in the Soviet Union" in ''[[#Courtois1999BlackBook|The Black Book]]'' p. 98.</ref>在1919年的前几个月，10,000到12,000名[[哥萨克|哥萨克]]被处死<ref name="mass terror">Peter Holquist. "[http://www.persee.fr/web/revues/home/prescript/article/cmr_1252-6576_1997_num_38_1_2486 Conduct merciless mass terror": decossackization on the Don, 1919] {{Wayback|url=http://www.persee.fr/web/revues/home/prescript/article/cmr_1252-6576_1997_num_38_1_2486 |date=20091204190025 }}"</ref><ref>[[共产主义政权下的大屠杀#Figes1997PeoplesTragedy|Figes (1997) ''A People's Tragedy'']] p. 660.{{Verify source|date=2011年6月}} <!-- this claimed to be a 1998 edition of penguin?  Penguin NY versus Penguin UK? different ISBN 0-14-024364-X.  needs page number verification against the 1997 source--></ref>，而且更多的人被驅逐，在他們的村庄被夷为平地後。<ref name="Gellately">[[#Gellately2007LeninStalinandHitler|Gellately (2007) ''Lenin, Stalin, and Hitler'']] pp. 70–71.</ref>

====大清洗（叶若夫时期）====
{{Main|大清洗}}

斯大林试图巩固自己作为苏联领导人的地位，导致对各类人拘留和执行死刑的數字劇增，1937–38年达到高潮（这段时期有时被称作[[叶若夫|叶若夫]]时期），并且一直持续到1953年斯大林逝世。其中有约700,000人从脑后枪决，<ref>Barry McLoughlin (2002) "Mass Operations of the NKVD, 1937–1938: a survey." in ''Stalin's Terror: High Politics and Mass Repression in the Soviet Union'' eds. Barry McLoughlin, Kevin McDermott [?]: Palgrave Macmillan, [//books.google.com/?id=8yorTJl1QEoC&pg=PA141 p. 141]. ISBN 1-4039-0119-8.</ref>其他人在“调查拘禁”的拷打中<ref>[[#Gellately2007LeninStalinandHitler|Gellately (2007) ''Lenin, Stalin, and Hitler'']] p. 256.</ref>以及在[[古拉格|古拉格]]中因为饥饿、疾病、暴露和过度劳累死去。<ref name="Ellman2">{{Cite journal|last=Ellman|first=Michael|title=Soviet Repression Statistics: Some Comments|journal=Europea-Asia Studies|volume=34|issue=7|year=2002|pages=1151–1172 |quote=The best estimate that can currently be made of the number of repression deaths in 1937–38 is the range 950,000–1.2 million, i.e., about a million. This estimate should be used by historians, teachers, and journalists concerned with twentieth century Russian—and world—history}}</ref>

逮捕行动通常根据[[第58号条款|反革命法]]实施，其中包括未报告叛逆行为，以及1937年修正案中未履行指定职责的行为。内务人民委员会国家安全部（GUGB NKVD）在1936年10月到1938年11月的调查行动中至少有1,710,000人被捕，并有724,000人被处决。<ref>[http://www.memo.ru/history/y1937/hronika1936_1939/xronika.html N.G. Okhotin, A.B. Roginsky ''"Great Terror": Brief Chronology] {{Wayback|url=http://www.memo.ru/history/y1937/hronika1936_1939/xronika.html |date=20100127135632 }} [[Memorial_(society)|Memorial]], 2007</ref>

[[File:Vinnycia16.jpg|thumb]]，1937–38年间的{{link-en|苏联的万人坑|Mass graves in the Soviet Union|万人坑}}被揭开，并有上百具尸体被挖出以讓家属辨认。<ref>[[#Courtois1999BlackBook|Courtois (1999) ''The Black Book'']] photographic insert following p. 202.</ref>]]

至于对神职人员的迫害，{{le|迈克尔·埃尔曼|Michael Ellman}}称“……1937–38年亦曾打击俄国正教会及其他宗教的神父（Binner & Junge 2004）或许同样也能当作是灭绝”。<ref name="Ellman"/>[[亚历山大·尼古拉耶维奇·雅科夫列夫|亚历山大·尼古拉耶维奇·雅科夫列夫]]引用教会的文件估计超过100,000名牧师、修士和修女在此期间被处死。<ref>[[#Yakovlev2002CenturyofViolence|Yakovlev (2002) ''Century of Violence'']] p. 165;<br/>See also: [[#Pipes2001Communism|Pipes (2001) ''Communism'']] p. 66.</ref>

前“[[富农_(俄国)|富农]]”和他们的家庭构成了死难者的大多数，有669,929人被捕，并有376,202人被处死。<ref name="Orlando Figes The Whisperers 2007, page 240">[[Orlando_Figes|Orlando Figes]]. ''The Whisperers: Private Life in Stalin's Russia.'' Metropolitan Books, 2007. ISBN 0-08050-7461-9, [//books.google.com/books?id=sge44FaZDREC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA240#v=onepage&q&f=false page 240]</ref>

====内务人民委员会的国内行动====
{{Main|内务人民委员会的国内行动}}

1930年代，[[内务人民委员会|内务人民委员会]]在国内掀起了一系列的行动，针对一些有反革命活动嫌疑的“国家特遣队”。<ref name="Ellman">[http://www1.fee.uva.nl/pp/mjellman/ Michael Ellman] {{Wayback|url=http://www1.fee.uva.nl/pp/mjellman/ |date=20071014232729 }}, [http://www.paulbogdanor.com/left/soviet/famine/ellman1933.pdf Stalin and the Soviet Famine of 1932–33 Revisited] {{Wayback|url=http://www.paulbogdanor.com/left/soviet/famine/ellman1933.pdf |date=20150415231308 }} ''Europe-Asia Studies'', [[Routledge|Routledge]]. Vol. 59, No. 4, June 2007, 663–693. [[PDF|PDF]] file</ref>总共有350,000人被捕，并有247,157人被处死。<ref name="Montefiore229">[[#Montefiore2005CourtoftheRedTsar|Montefiore (2005) ''Court of the Red Tsar'']] p. 229.</ref>其中{{link-en|内务人民委员会的波兰人行动|Polish operation of the NKVD|波兰人行动}}针对已不存在的[[波兰军事组织|波兰军事组织]]，其逮捕和處死的人數似乎是最高的，有140,000人被捕，并有111,000人被处死。<ref name="Ellman"/>即使这些行动按照联合国公約可以定为种族灭绝，<ref name="Ellman"/>或按[[蒙蒂菲奥里|蒙蒂菲奥里]]定为“小规模种族灭绝”，<ref name="Montefiore229"/>对这些事件还是没有权威的法律裁定。<ref name="Ellman"/>

====蒙古的大清洗====
{{Main|蒙古的斯大林主义镇压}}

1937年夏秋两季，[[约瑟夫·斯大林|约瑟夫·斯大林]]安排NKVD特工去[[蒙古人民共和国|蒙古人民共和国]]并協助[[霍爾洛·喬巴山|霍爾洛·喬巴山]]策划了[[蒙古的斯大林主义镇压|蒙古大清洗]]，<ref name="Kuromiya pg2">Hiroaki Kuromiya, ''The Voices of the Dead: Stalin's Great Terror in the 1930s.'' [[耶鲁大学出版社|耶鲁大学出版社]], December 24, 2007. ISBN 0-300-12389-2. p. 2</ref>其中有22,000<ref name="Thirty thousand">{{Cite web |url=http://www.chriskaplonski.com/downloads/bullets.pdf |title=Christopher Kaplonski, ''Thirty thousand bullets'', in: ''Historical Injustice and Democratic Transition in Eastern Asia and Northern Europe'', London 2002, pp. 155–168 |accessdate=2014-10-11 |archive-date=2011-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110511044943/http://www.chriskaplonski.com/downloads/bullets.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>到35,000<ref name="Death Tolls">{{Cite web |url=http://users.erols.com/mwhite28/warstat5.htm#Mong2 |title=Twentieth Century Atlas – Death Tolls |accessdate=2014-10-11 |archive-date=2019-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191022115708/http://users.erols.com/mwhite28/warstat5.htm#Mong2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>人被处死。大约18,000名牺牲者是[[喇嘛|喇嘛]]。<ref name="Thirty thousand"/>

====苏联在二战期间的屠杀====
