== 对屠杀及否定屠杀的诉讼 ==
[[File:Katyń,_ekshumacja_ofiar.jpg|thumb]]1943年发掘的尸体。[[国际红十字会|国际红十字会]]派代表拍摄。]]

埃塞俄比亚前领导人[[海尔·马里亚姆·门格斯图|海尔·马里亚姆·门格斯图]]被定为[[种族灭绝罪|种族灭绝罪]]、[[战争罪|战争罪]]和[[危害人类罪|危害人类罪]]，埃塞俄比亚法院以其在[[红色恐怖_(埃塞俄比亚)|红色恐怖]]中的角色，並且作為被起訴这些罪名的[[红色高棉|红色高棉]]最高级别的现存者，對他判處死刑。<ref name=ApBbcKr>Staff, [http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/asia-pacific/7002053.stm Senior Khmer Rouge leader charged] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/asia-pacific/7002053.stm |date=20170904055210 }}, BBC September 19, 2007</ref><ref name="Mengistu found guilty">{{Cite news | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/6171429.stm | title=BBC, "Mengistu found guilty of genocide," 12 December 2006 | date=December 12, 2006 | accessdate=January 2, 2010 | work=BBC News | archive-date=2018-07-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180708040238/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/6171429.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="HRW">[http://hrw.org/english/docs/1999/11/29/ethiop5495.htm Backgrounders: Ethiopian Dictator Mengistu Haile Mariam] {{Wayback|url=http://hrw.org/english/docs/1999/11/29/ethiop5495.htm |date=20081102144901 }} [[Human_Rights_Watch|Human Rights Watch]], 1999</ref><ref>Tsegaye Tadesse. [http://www.redorbit.com/news/international/512182/verdict_due_for_ethiopias_exdictator_mengistu/ Verdict due for Ethiopia's ex-dictator Mengistu] {{Wayback|url=http://www.redorbit.com/news/international/512182/verdict_due_for_ethiopias_exdictator_mengistu/ |date=20200419003409 }} [[Reuters|Reuters]], 2006</ref><ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/7420212.stm Court Sentences Mengistu to Death] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/7420212.stm |date=20170710025302 }} [[BBC|BBC]], May 26, 2008.</ref>然而，没有共产主义国家或政府部门被判为种族灭绝罪。埃塞俄比亚法律跟联合国及其他的定义有別，它定義种族灭绝罪是企圖清除政治群體，而不光是族裔群体。从這种意义上说它接近于政治灭绝罪的區分。<ref name=RGP>Barbara Harff, "Recognizing Genocides and Politicides", in ''Genocide Watch'' 27 (Helen Fein ed., 1992) pp.37,38</ref>

根据[[捷克共和国|捷克共和国]]法律，公开否认、质疑、赞成或者企图辩护纳粹和共产主义种族灭绝或者纳粹和共产主义其他罪行的人会被处以6个月到3年徒刑。<ref name="czech">{{Cite web |url=http://www.jcpa.org/JCPA/Templates/ShowPage.asp?DRIT=5&DBID=1&LNGID=1&TMID=111&FID=624&PID=0&IID=2202&TTL=Expanding_Holocaust_Denial_and_Legislation_Against_It |title=Expanding Holocaust Denial and Legislation |access-date=2014-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111104025927/http://www.jcpa.org/JCPA/Templates/ShowPage.asp?DRIT=5&DBID=1&LNGID=1&TMID=111&FID=624&PID=0&IID=2202&TTL=Expanding_Holocaust_Denial_and_Legislation_Against_It |archive-date=2011-11-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>2005年3月，波兰[[波兰共和国下议院|下议院]]一致要求俄罗斯把斯大林手下[[内务人民委员会|内务人民委员会]]处死21,000名波兰军事组织成员及思想领袖的[[卡廷大屠杀|卡廷大屠杀]]定为种族灭绝罪。<ref name="polishembassy310305">波兰政府声明：[http://www.polishembassy.ca/news_details.asp?nid=230 Senate pays tribute to Katyn victims – 3/31/2005] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20050420045807/http://www.polishembassy.ca/news_details.asp?nid=230 |date=2005-04-20 }}</ref>俄罗斯联邦检察官办公室的亚历山大·萨文科夫回应道：“种族灭绝的版本已经檢視过，而且我的坚定信念是绝对没有基礎去從法律条款談論這件事。”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cracow-life.com/news/news/374-Russia_Says_Katyn_Executions_Not_Genocide |title=Russia Says Katyn Executions Not Genocide |accessdate=2014-10-11 |archive-date=2012-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120225163728/http://www.cracow-life.com/news/news/374-Russia_Says_Katyn_Executions_Not_Genocide |dead-url=no }}</ref>2010年3月，{{link-en|纪念碑组织|Memorial (society)}}呼吁俄罗斯总统[[德米特里·梅德韦杰夫|德米特里·梅德韦杰夫]]公开谴责大屠杀是反人类罪行。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://politicom.moldova.org/news/memorial-calls-on-medvedev-to-denounce-katyn-as-crime-against-humanity-206909-eng.html |title=Memorial calls on Medvedev to denounce Katyn as crime against humanity  |accessdate=2014-10-11 |archive-date=2011-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928052636/http://politicom.moldova.org/news/memorial-calls-on-medvedev-to-denounce-katyn-as-crime-against-humanity-206909-eng.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2010年11月26日，俄罗斯[[国家杜马|国家杜马]]发布公告称档案材料“不仅揭开了他可怕的悲剧的规模，而且提供了证據說明在卡廷犯下的罪行是直接来自斯大林和其他苏联领导人的命令。”<ref>Ellen Barry. [http://www.nytimes.com/2010/11/27/world/europe/27briefs-katyn.html Russia: Stalin Called Responsible for Katyn Killings] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/11/27/world/europe/27briefs-katyn.html |date=20201109033251 }}. [[纽约时报|纽约时报]], November 26, 2010.</ref>

2007年8月，[[爱沙尼亚|爱沙尼亚]][[苏联红军|红军]]老兵{{link-en|阿诺德·梅里|Arnold Meri}}和爱沙尼亚前总统的堂兄{{link-en|伦纳德·梅里|Lennart Meri}}面临爱沙尼亚當局的的种族灭绝指控，他們被指1949年在[[希乌马岛|希乌马岛]]参与了{{link-en|苏联在爱沙尼亚的驱逐|Soviet deportations from Estonia|对爱沙尼亚人的驱逐}}。<ref>[http://www.balticguide.ee/index.php/a641 Entisen presidentin serkkua syytetään neuvostoajan kyydityksistä] {{Wayback|url=http://www.balticguide.ee/index.php/a641 |date=20060516180039 }} – ''[[Baltic_Guide|Baltic Guide]]''</ref><ref>[http://www.b92.net/eng/news/globe-article.php?yyyy=2007&mm=08&dd=23&nav_category=117&version=print Estonian charged with Communist genocide] {{Wayback|url=http://www.b92.net/eng/news/globe-article.php?yyyy=2007&mm=08&dd=23&nav_category=117&version=print |date=20110607181514 }} ''[[International_Herald_Tribune|International Herald Tribune]]'', August 23, 2007</ref>审判因为梅里2009年3月27日逝世而中断，他死時89岁。梅里否认这一指控，认为那是有政治动机的诽谤：“我不认为我自己犯有种族灭绝罪”，他说。<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/7978111.stm | work=BBC News | title=Estonian war figure laid to rest | date=April 2, 2009 | accessdate=May 12, 2010 | archive-date=2009-04-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090404111252/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/7978111.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2010年7月26日，超过14,000人受到折磨并被谋杀（多数在附近的[[琼邑克|琼邑克]]）的[[民主柬埔寨|民主柬埔寨]][[吐斯廉屠杀博物馆|S-21集中营]]的监狱长[[康克由|康克由]]（又称杜赫同志）被判为危害人类罪并判处35年监禁。他的刑期减少到19年是因为他已经入狱11年。<ref>[http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-fg-cambodia-khmer-rouge-20100727,0,4747344.story Sentence reduced for former Khmer Rouge prison chief] {{Wayback|url=http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-fg-cambodia-khmer-rouge-20100727,0,4747344.story |date=20100731012205 }}. [[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]], July 27, 2010</ref>

